’ђђЪ)Title: title: bits shr
Path: Examples
Content:
Shift right a number with 2 bits
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 8 | bits shr 2
2

```
Shift right a list of numbers
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [15 35 2] | bits shr 2
в•­в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”¬в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв•®
в”‚ 0 в”‚ 3 в”‚
в”‚ 1 в”‚ 8 в”‚
